Messages sent to this bot containing any audio files (including voice messages) will be recognized as text by default, but there is also a choice among the available functions. At the moment, not all audio formats may be supported for recognition.

Function speech recognition is implemented using the SpeechRecognition library for Python, which allows you to use various available APIs for speech-to-text recognition. The bot itself uses the Google Speech Recognition API for recognition. The shazamio library is also used, which is a version of the Shazam API for Python that allows recognition, and in the future, search for songs using the recorded audio file.

The bot, like a regular user, can receive information up to 2000 MiB in the way it was developed using pyrogram, which allows you to expand the limits of the Bot API by interacting directly with MTProto and Telegram API.

